== Welcome to Groupswiki

Groupswiki is a Wiki-engine that tries to take away the barriers from 
non-technical users contributing to a wiki. It was built by Ben Nolan
(bnolan@gmail.com).

Groupswiki is AGPL Licensed.

You can get a hosted Groupswiki at www.groupswiki.com.

== Installation

You will need the following to use groupswiki:

 * Ruby 1.8.5+
 * MySQL server

And the following gems:

 * rails - we use version 1.2.3
 * tidy - we use version 1.1.2
 * minimagick or rmagick
 
Once you've got these - run the following commands on the command-
line to set up your installation:

  mysqladmin -u root create groupswiki_production
  RAILS_ENV=production rake db:migrate
  RAILS_ENV=production rake db:fixtures:load
  RAILS_ENV=production script/server
  
The wiki should now be available via your webbrowser at:

  http://localhost:3000/

